---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';

export const prerender = true;
---

<Base title="Support" description="Support HN HRCB — help keep the evaluations running">
  <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
    <tr class="athing">
      <td style="padding: 12px 10px 4px;">
        <span style="font-size:13pt; color:#98a8a8;">Support HN HRCB</span>
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 4px 10px 24px;">
        <div style="color:#5b7279; font-size:9pt; line-height:1.8; max-width:580px;">
          <p>This project is built and maintained by a single developer — a software engineer for roughly a decade, now retired and navigating a long-term disability determination while managing ongoing medical challenges. Thanks to an <a href="https://claude.ai/code" style="color:#d56500;">Anthropic Claude Code</a> subscription, I'm able to keep building — and this is how I spend that ability: community service tools that make human rights visible in the places where builders already spend their time.</p>

          <p>HN HRCB evaluates Hacker News stories against the <a href="https://www.un.org/en/about-us/universal-declaration-of-human-rights" style="color:#d56500;">UN Universal Declaration of Human Rights</a> using large language models. Each evaluation costs real API credits — multiple models, multiple passes, a continuous 24/7 pipeline. There are no ads, no tracking, no paywalls, and no VC funding. The entire service runs on personal savings and donations.</p>

          <p>Right now, I simply can't afford the API credits to evaluate as many stories as I'd like. Every dollar directly translates into more evaluations — more stories scored, more patterns surfaced, more of the invisible made visible. Even a small contribution makes a real difference.</p>

          <p>If you find this useful — as a research tool, a lens on media bias, or just an interesting way to think about the news — anything helps. It means more than I can say.</p>

          <div style="margin:24px 0; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:10px; max-width:360px;">
            <form action="https://www.paypal.com/donate" method="post" target="_blank" id="support-donate-form">
              <input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="56GCFHDZHB7AJ" />
              <button type="submit" style="width:100%; background:rgba(234,179,8,0.2); border:1px solid rgba(234,179,8,0.4); color:#eab308; cursor:pointer; padding:12px 28px; font-size:11pt; border-radius:6px; font-weight:bold;">
                Donate via PayPal
              </button>
            </form>
            <a href="https://github.com/sponsors/kashifshah" target="_blank" id="support-sponsors-link" style="display:block; background:rgba(139,92,246,0.15); border:1px solid rgba(139,92,246,0.3); color:#a78bfa; padding:12px 28px; font-size:11pt; border-radius:6px; font-weight:bold; text-decoration:none; text-align:center;">
              ♥ GitHub Sponsors
            </a>
          </div>

          <p>Already donated? <a href="#" id="support-mark-donated" style="color:#5b7279; text-decoration:underline;">Click here to skip the donation prompt</a> for 7 days.</p>

          <p style="margin-top:24px; color:#1a5568;">
            The source code is on <a href="https://github.com/kashifshah/unudhr" style="color:#d56500;">GitHub</a>. Contributions and issue reports are welcome.
          </p>

          <div style="margin-top:32px; padding-top:16px; border-top:1px solid rgba(91,114,121,0.2);">
            <a href="https://anthropic.com" target="_blank" style="display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; text-decoration:none; color:#5b7279; font-size:8pt; opacity:0.7;" title="Built with Claude Code by Anthropic">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="vertical-align:middle;">
                <path d="M16.5 3L21 12l-4.5 9h-3L18 12l-4.5-9h3zM7.5 3L3 12l4.5 9h3L6 12l4.5-9h-3z" fill="currentColor"/>
              </svg>
              Built with Claude · I stand with Anthropic
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <script is:inline>
    document.getElementById('support-donate-form')?.addEventListener('submit', function() {
      localStorage.setItem('hrcb_donated', new Date().toISOString());
    });
    document.getElementById('support-sponsors-link')?.addEventListener('click', function() {
      localStorage.setItem('hrcb_donated', new Date().toISOString());
    });
    document.getElementById('support-mark-donated')?.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
      e.preventDefault();
      localStorage.setItem('hrcb_donated', new Date().toISOString());
      var el = document.getElementById('support-mark-donated');
      if (el) {
        el.textContent = 'Done — thank you!';
        el.style.color = '#16a34a';
        el.style.pointerEvents = 'none';
      }
    });
  </script>
</Base>
